<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,549,1247]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
Closely resembling 
<taxonomicName box="[432,523,736,761]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Empoasca" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="peba" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[432,523,736,761]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">E. peba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[530,597,735,761]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[530,597,735,761]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">n. sp.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
except pygofer process in lateral view shorter and less strongly curved than in 
<taxonomicName box="[240,330,773,798]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Empoasca" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="peba">
<emphasis box="[240,330,773,798]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">E. peba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation box="[347,419,773,799]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="8.[151,255,1773,1797]" captionTargetBox="[355,1231,1299,1752]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[349,1238,1292,1758]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 4. Empoasca affinipeba n. sp. a. genital capsule, lateral view; i. pygofer process, ventral view" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/196392/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
Fig. 
<number box="[402,419,773,799]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" value="4.0">4</number>
</figureCitation>
a); in caudo-ventral view, short, angled mediad from base (not bowed strongly mediad nor crossing at midline); apically constricted, thence expanded, thence tapered to a narrow point - producing a “candle-flame” appearance (
<figureCitation box="[485,556,848,874]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="8.[151,255,1773,1797]" captionTargetBox="[355,1231,1299,1752]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[349,1238,1292,1758]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 4. Empoasca affinipeba n. sp. a. genital capsule, lateral view; i. pygofer process, ventral view" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/196392/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
Fig. 
<number box="[539,556,848,874]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" value="4.0">
<date box="[539,556,848,874]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">4</date>
</number>
</figureCitation>
i).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
